{
  "stem": "5496.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some beautiful smells of pastry came around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we, with big eyes, we were looking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Will we ever be in a warm and clean place ourself?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's about the only thing I remember of it, so it must have been December.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What-- what kept you going?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What sustained you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hard to say.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really don't know, because I don't think our thinking was absolutely clear, to say the least.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were already starving.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was just mechanically, that we could get up, and do, and come.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I don't think we gave any philosophical thought to anything-- at least, not in my case.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was a kid, and I was emaciated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I started to look like a child.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And up until the day that we left, and all I remembered, they herded us to these columns, and we were on foot.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we left [INAUDIBLE] on the infamous death march, which eventually led, then, to Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The shoe-- we had, like, straw, and some girls had wooden shoes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What I had, I haven't got the slightest idea.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But whatever it was, it obviously wasn't much, because during the march, we would-- they would herd us at night, usually, into-- must have been horse's stalls, because it was full of straw.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we would sleep there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we would take some of that straw, and I know that one of the [INAUDIBLE] would come, and my feet were frozen.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Aunt Rose took my feet in her mouth to warm them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the next morning, they would send the dogs again, because a lot of girls try to hide in the straw.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
